This package bundles tokenizer assets derived from official Hugging Face repositories under the MiniMaxAI organization:
- MiniMaxAI/MiniMax-M2 tokenizer.json
- MiniMaxAI/MiniMax-M1-40k tokenizer.json
- MiniMaxAI/MiniMax-Text-01-hf tokenizer.json

The following supported model names are aliases confirmed to reuse those bundled tokenizer assets and are not shipped as separate snapshots:
- MiniMaxAI/MiniMax-M2.1
- MiniMaxAI/MiniMax-M2.5
- MiniMaxAI/MiniMax-M1-80k
- MiniMaxAI/MiniMax-M1-40k-hf
- MiniMaxAI/MiniMax-M1-80k-hf
- MiniMaxAI/MiniMax-Text-01

This package also ships NOTICE to satisfy the attribution requirement from the
MiniMax Model License used by MiniMaxAI/MiniMax-Text-01-hf.

See LICENSE and NOTICE for the full license text and attribution notices that
apply to this package and its bundled assets.
